<li>A few drops of <a href="/wiki/Worcestershire_sauce" title="Worcestershire sauce">Worcestershire sauce</a> and <a href="/wiki/Maggi" title="Maggi">Maggi sauce</a> or <a href="/wiki/Soy_sauce" title="Soy sauce">Soy sauce</a> or <a href="/wiki/Teriyaki_sauce" title="Teriyaki sauce" class="mw-redirect">Teriyaki sauce</a> and <a href="/wiki/Hot_sauce" title="Hot sauce">Hot sauce</a> and Fresh squeezed lime</li>
